subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Harvick, the eighth and final qualifier with a chance to advance to Nascar’s final four next week at Homestead-Miami Speedway, won Sunday’s race at Phoenix International Raceway.
